Gentlemen;

We will be conducting a Leader's Reconnaissance of the Mt. Carmel Site
Defense area of operations. These exercise operations will occur on 13-15
MAY 26. This reconnaissance will be conducted in order to meet the
installation POC (Mr. Armstrong) and answer any RFI's and address any
concerns which the group may have regarding expected and anticipated
operations during the TNMAN-26 exercise.

I anticipate that the team that will meet is:

COL Noah Roark, CDR 3 RGT TNSG
LTC Steve Estes, CDR 2 RGT TNSG
CSM Michael Seals, CSM RGT TNSG
LTC John Sheaf, S3 3 RGT TNSG
MAJ Lyle Crosby, CDR 3 Bn / 3 RGT, TNSG
1LT Aaron Overton, Asst S3 3 RGT TNSG
SFC Adam Acosta, TNSG IRR / State Defense Force Foundation

We will link up at the Walgreens parking lot, 4500 W Stone Dr, Kingsport,
TN 37660 NLT 061455RMAY26 and proceed to the linkup point at the Main Gate.

Should you have any questions or concerns, please let me know.

-- 
V/R

JOHN T. SHEAF
LTC, TNSG
S3, 3 RGT
717.673.6177
john.sheaf@tnstateguard.org

